### 1. 소셜 로그인 - 구글 (신규 가입)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "provider": "GOOGLE",
  "socialId": "google-real-12345",
  "email": "realuser@gmail.com",
  "name": "실제유저",
  "socialEmail": "realuser@gmail.com",
  "profileImageUrl": "https://example.com/profile.jpg"
}

